These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, almond-milk, fanta
4 different pets are kept: turtle, pony, rat, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
3. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | fanta | almond-milk |
| Pet        | turtle | pony   | rabbit | rat    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, drama, animation, documentary
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, australian, chinese, pakistani
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the malaysian is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the chinese is in an odd position##4
4. the malaysian is the person watching epic movies##1
5. the australian is on the right of the chinese##1
6. the malaysian is the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | epic  | drama  | documentary |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | malaysian | chinese | australian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, pumpkin, lime, avocado
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, mystery, superhero, martial-arts
1. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
2. the person eating lime is in an even position##4
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | avocado | lime | pumpkin    | pineapple      |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero        | martial-arts     | adventure | mystery |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, writing, photography, collecting
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, classical, gospel, ambient
1. the person who's hobby is writing is between the fan of electronic and the fan of ambient##2
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the fan of gospel is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
5. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | collecting | puzzles | writing | photography |
| Music-Genre   | gospel       | electronic   | classical    | ambient  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, metal, soul, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, nigerian, chinese, pakistani
1. the fan of soul is on the right of the pakistani##1
2. the nigerian is the fan of trance##1
3. the chinese is on the right of the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
5. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
6. the dutch is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | rock    | soul   | trance       |
| Nationality   | dutch | pakistani | chinese | nigerian |

