2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the train##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person driving the subway is the person watching documentary movies##1
5. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
6. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
