.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, bartender, freelancer, engineer
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, mouse, frog, horse
1. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the bartender##3
2. the engineer is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the engineer##3
4. the engineer is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
5. the police-officer is between the engineer and the bartender##2
6. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the mouse is between the police-officer and the owner of the frog##2
8. the police-officer is on the left or right of the bartender##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | bartender | police-officer      | engineer | freelancer |
| Pet   | rabbit  | horse | mouse    | frog            |

