4 different pets are kept: goat, hedgehog, rat, lizard
1. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating radish##1
3. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person eating eggplant##2
4. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating eggplant is the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | nectarine | radish   | plum | eggplant |
| Pet    | lizard     | hedgehog | goat     | rat  |

