.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, tea, coffee
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, trance, funk, metal
1. the person drinking milk is the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of techno is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the fan of metal is between the fan of techno and the person drinking tea##2
4. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | tea   | milk | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | funk | trance | metal        | techno    |

