.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, pepper, peach, apple
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, gospel, jazz, d&b
1. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of pop##1
2. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
3. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
4. the person eating orange is on the far right##1
5. the person eating peach is between the fan of gospel and the fan of jazz##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | apple | pepper  | peach  | orange |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | jazz | pop | gospel   |

