.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, filmmaking, reading, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, water-polo, baseball, cycling
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | writing | filmmaking         | rock-climbing   | reading |
| Sport   | baseball    | water-polo | cycling | tennis   |

