.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, baking, card-games, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, sailing, climbing, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
5. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | baking | writing | card-games    | dancing |
| Sport   | handball   | climbing  | soccer | sailing     |

