.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, dancing, reading, video-games
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, canadian, dutch, argentine
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
3. the canadian is the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the dutch is on the left or right of the canadian##3
5. the canadian is between the argentine and the dutch##2
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games   | reading | writing | dancing    |
| Nationality   | dutch | canadian  | argentine     | mexican |

