.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, cola, almond-milk
There 4 different types of food: almond-milkmelon, broccoli, papaya, asparagus
1. the person eating broccoli is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
5. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person eating papaya is in an even position##4
7. the person eating almond-milkmelon is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | hot-chocolate    | cola       | juice |
| Food       | broccoli  | papaya | asparagus | almond-milkmelon  |

