.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, argentine, dutch, australian
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, bike, ship
1. the malaysian is on the left of the australian##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the dutch##1
5. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | argentine | dutch | malaysian  | australian |
| Transport     | snowmobile      | bike       | airplane | ship     |

