.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, videographer, lawyer, teacher
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, snowmobile, bike, boat
1. the videographer is in an even position##4
2. the videographer is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
3. the person driving the snowmobile is between the social-worker and the person driving the roller##2
4. the videographer is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the teacher##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | social-worker | lawyer   | teacher | videographer |
| Transport   | boat          | snowmobile | roller         | bike  |

 